thread.title: Earle Shenk

author: Earle Shenk
title: Earle Shenk
text: I've been a coffe-holic since 1972 when I lived within walking distance to the original Peet's Coffee in North Berkeley. I've enjoyed malita, french press, cold press, cheap espresso, now fully automatic espresso machine purchased at WholeLatteLove (my 2nd machine from them). I purchase all my coffee from WLL, and will continue. Super helpful website as well!!
